message.msgid: Please enter the valid User name and Password provided by your ISP.
message.msgstr: Please enter the valid User name and Password provided by your ISP.

message.msgid: Start time must be earlier than end time!
message.msgstr: Start time must be earlier than end time!

message.msgid: Please enter a valid server address!
message.msgstr: Please enter a valid server address!

message.msgid: Please enter an MTU value between 256 and 1500!
message.msgstr: Please enter an MTU value between 256 and 1500!

message.msgid: The default value is 1500. Do not modify it unless required by your ISP.
message.msgstr: The default value is 1500. Do not modify it unless required by your ISP.

message.msgid: The default value is 1492. Do not modify it unless required by your ISP.
message.msgstr: The default value is 1492. Do not modify it unless required by your ISP.

message.msgid: Select the corresponding connection mode according to your situation.
message.msgstr: Select the corresponding connection mode according to your situation.

message.msgid: Connect automatically: Connect automatically to the Internet after rebooting the system or connection failure.
message.msgstr: Connect automatically: Connect automatically to the Internet after rebooting the system or connection failure.

message.msgid: Connect on demand: Re-establish your connection to the Internet when there’s data transmitting.
message.msgstr: Connect on demand: Re-establish your connection to the Internet when there’s data transmitting.
Note: To use the "Connect During Specified Time Period" mode, you must set the "Time Settings" in "Tools" first.

message.msgid: Only enter this information if instructed by ISP.
message.msgstr: Only enter this information if instructed by ISP.

message.msgid: Connect Manually: Require the user to manually connect to the Internet before each session.
message.msgstr: Connect Manually: Require the user to manually connect to the Internet before each session.

message.msgid: Connect During Specified Time Period: Connect automatically to Internet during a specified time length.
message.msgstr: Connect During Specified Time Period: Connect automatically to Internet during a specified time length.

message.msgid: MTU value! It must be numeric
message.msgstr: MTU value! It must be numeric

message.msgid: Please specify a valid MAC address!
message.msgstr: Please specify a valid MAC address!

message.msgid: The MAC address of %s is invalid! Please specify a valid MAC address!
message.msgstr: The MAC address of %s is invalid! Please specify a valid MAC address!

message.msgid: Router's IP Address has been changed! Please update related settings!
message.msgstr: Router's IP Address has been changed! Please update related settings!

message.msgid: You have changed the IP address of this router, please click on OK to confirm this change. The router will reboot. After reboot, if the webpage doesn't update automatically, please renew your computer's connection to the router and then use the new IP address to login.
message.msgstr: You have changed the IP address of this router, please click on "OK" to confirm this change. The router will reboot. After reboot, if the webpage doesn't update automatically, please renew your computer's connection to the router and then use the new IP address to login.

message.msgid: This page is used to set the basic network parameters for LAN.
message.msgstr: This page is used to set the basic network parameters for LAN.

message.msgid: Note: To activate new settings, you must reboot the device.
message.msgstr: Note: To activate new settings, you must reboot the device.

message.msgid: Please enter an IP pool start address that is smaller than the IP pool end address.
message.msgstr: Please enter an IP pool start address that is smaller than the IP pool end address.

message.msgid: Up to 16 Address Reservations are supported!
message.msgstr: Up to 16 Address Reservations are supported!

message.msgid: Please don't add the LAN IP address or the IP address that already exists in the address Reservation table!
message.msgstr: Please don't add the LAN IP address or the IP address that already exists in the address Reservation table!

message.msgid: Please don't add MAC address that already exists in the address Reservation table!
message.msgstr: Please don't add MAC address that already exists in the address Reservation table!
